HEADWORD: Momier
<hw>Mom"i*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>m⟦ocir⟧mier</ets>, fr. OF. <ets>momer</ets>, <ets>mommer</ets>, to
